summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Nichols Garden Tracts; Churchill's Suburban Villa; City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 8400278; Wedgwood Addition; Richmond Highlands; Merrick's Acre Tracts Division No. 2; Cedar Park; Innis Arden No. 4; Section 5, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
